            "pub_date": "2026-03-30 18:17:01",
            "source": "yahoo_finance_asia",
            "kind": 1,
            "language": "zh-HK"
        },
        {
            "title": "財經｜中銀(03988)去年多賺2% 息降至11.69分",
            "description": "<div class=\"atoms\"><figure class=\"mb-module-gap\"><div class=\"mx-auto w-fit max-w-full\"><img alt=\"財經｜中銀(03988)去年多賺2% 息降至11.69分\" class=\"rounded-lg\" height=\"502\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://s.yimg.com/ny/api/res/1.2/La7gZ15XzW1pdZUwE2YseQ--/YXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjt3PTk2MDtoPTUwMg--/https://media.zenfs.com/ko/fortune_insight_694/dbddec0f78d2a1ab4bc25a6950c04ffb\" width=\"960\"/><figcaption class=\"text-px14 text-dolphin mt-2 wrap-anywhere\" style=\"max-width:960px\">財經｜中銀(03988)去年多賺2% 息降至11.69分</figcaption></div></figure><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">中國銀行(03988)公布，截至去年底止年度業績，股東應佔盈利2430.21億元(人民幣‧下同)，按年增長2.18%。每股基本盈利0.74元。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">集團派末期息每股0.1169元，按年減少3.87%；連同中期息0.1094元，全年共派息0.2263元，減少6.64%。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">期內，營業收入6598.66億元，按年升4.28%。淨利息收入4407.05億元，跌1.83%；淨息差1.26%，下降14個基點，主要受境內人民幣貸款市場報價利率(LPR)下調，以及外幣市場利率下降等因素影響，生息資產平均收益率下降49個基點。</p><div class=\"bg-toast-background -mx-5 -mt-2 mb-3 pb-3 md:-mx-0 lg:mx-auto lg:w-[300px] lg:pb-0\"><div class=\"text-px14 text-gandalf py-1 text-center leading-5\">廣告</div><div class=\"mx-auto text-center min-w-[300px] min-h-[250px]\" id=\"sda-inbody-b5dca827-4ccd-3571-b4ae-e5ef1aff1ba2-1-iframe\"><div class=\"bg-dirty-seagull text-px12 text-dolphin mx-auto hidden items-center justify-center only:flex w-[300px] h-[250px]\">廣告</div></div></div><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">非利息收入2191.61億元，按年升19.21%。其中，手續費及佣金收支淨額822.37億元，增長7.37%。其他非利息收入1369.24億元，增長27.67%，主要是該行主動把握金融市場波動機遇，淨交易收入及貴金屬銷售收入增長較好。至於信用減值損失1020.04億元，減少0.45%。</p><div class=\"recommendation-contents\"><div class=\"bg-marshmallow mb-2 h-[30px] w-[80px] rounded-lg\"></div><div class=\"no-scrollbar -mx-5 mb-5 flex overflow-hidden overflow-x-auto md:-mx-2 lg:mb-3.5\"><div class=\"bg-marshmallow mr-2 ml-5 h-[92px] w-[calc(85%-28px)] flex-shrink-0 rounded-lg md:ml-2 md:w-[calc(85%-16px)] lg:h-[120px] lg:w-[calc(50%-16px)]\"></div><div class=\"bg-marshmallow mx-2 h-[92px] w-[85%] flex-shrink-0 rounded-lg lg:h-[120px] lg:w-[calc(50%-16px)]\"></div></div></div><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">去年底不良貸款率1.23%，較2024年底下滑0.02個百分點；不良貸款撥備覆蓋率200.37%，跌0.23個百分點。核心一級資本充足率12.53%，升0.33個百分點；一級資本充足率14.34%，跌0.04個百分點；資本充足率18.85%，升0.09個百分點</p></div>",
